											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Night. The player thrashes, feverish, clearly unwell. They're lying in a grassy field in the Astral Prison environment.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;In the distance, we hear crackling sounds (lighting) and what could be interpreted as a scream. It's Orpheus screaming." />
